Ryuhei Mori
<Image class="h-10" alt="ponunciation" src={pronounce}/>
</h1></div>
<div class="flex items-center ml-4">
<div class="mr-4">
<img  class="h-64" alt="portrait" src={ryuhei.src}/>
</div>
<div>
