<p class="mb-4">
Graduate School of Mathematics,<br>
Nagoya University.
</p>
<p class="mb-4">
mori[at]math.nagoya-u.ac.jp
</p>
<p>
<ul class="space-y-2">
<li><a href="http://orcid.org/0000-0001-5474-5145" aria-label="View ORCID record"><Image class="h-5 w-5 mr-1" alt="ORCID iD" src={orcid}/>0000-0001-5474-5145</a></li>
<li><a href="http://scholar.google.com/citations?user=7q_zIE0AAAAJ&amp;hl=en"><Image class="h-5 w-5 mr-1" alt="Google Scholar Citations" src={googlescholar}/>Google Scholar Citations</a></li>
